[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "それにしても、果ての大陸ってなんか寂しい場所だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00747",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、マナの結晶でキラキラしてるけど、\nなんというか……無機質な感じがするというか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00748",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ここには食べものとかあるのかしら？\n食べるものがないと動物も生きられないわよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00749",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ここに動物がいるなら、マナを食べて生きてたりして！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00750",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "っ！　みんな、ちょっと待って！\nあそこ、何かいるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00751",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えっ？　あれは……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00752",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あの、うにみたいにツンツンした生き物は……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00753",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "この子の仲間！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00754",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "この子、果ての大陸の生き物だったんだ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00755",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "前から気になってたけど、この生き物とレスナは\nどうやって出会ったのさ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00756",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "え？　どうやってって言われても、\n物心がついた時にはもう、ずっと一緒で……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00757",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "この子はね、レスナが祭壇に置かれていた時、\n寄り添うように一緒にいたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00758",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "引き離すのもな、と思って一緒に引き取って\n育てていたんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00759",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ねえ、あなた……仲間の元に帰りたい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00760",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あはは、レスナと一緒にいたいみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00761",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "この子も大切な仲間だもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00762",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん……これからも一緒だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00763",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]